### Asset erstellen

POST http://localhost:3000/api/commands
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "commandType" : "erstelleAsset",
  "isin" : "DE0005933956",
  "wkn" : "593395",
  "assetType" : "ETF",
  "name" : "iShare Core EURO STOCC 50 UCITS ETF (DE)"
}

